kpi_info.title: MAC-D SETUP ATTEMPT FOR DC-HSDPA
kpi_info.use: The number of attempted radio link setups/reconfigurations for DC-HSDPA MAC-d flow. Includes initial DC-HSDPA allocations, reconfigurations from SC-HSDPA to DC-HSDPA, handovers and serving cell changes. Also M1005C241 is updated along with this counter. UPDATED: When the RNC sends NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP REQUEST or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION PREPARE with information to configure DC-HSDPA MAC-d flow for the radio link. The counter is updated for the primary cell.
